<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,viewport-fit=cover">
<meta name="color-scheme" content="dark only">
<meta name="theme-color" content="#201b16">
<title>{{GROOM_NAME}} ♥ {{BRIDE_NAME}}의 결혼식에 초대합니다 | Moment Edit</title>
<meta name="description" content="{{GROOM_NAME}} · {{BRIDE_NAME}}, {{WEDDING_DATE_DISPLAY}} {{WEDDING_DAY_KOR}} {{WEDDING_TIME_DISPLAY}}. 함께해주시면 큰 기쁨이겠습니다.">
<meta name="author" content="Moment Edit">
<meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow">
